name: Medusa Giraxel
description:
Giraffe in form of Medusa
Snakes on his head made a Medusa Giraxel
Medusa in Yunani's mythologi was originally a beautifull woman, but one day she had an affair with Poseidon at Athena's temple. Athena got angry, she turned Medusa's hair into snakes and cursed Medusa : everyone who saw her eyes would turn to stone!
